":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"鍾意同中意係兩個意思嚟<br />\n<br />\n鍾意(zung1ji3) 鍾=喜歡，例: 一見鍾情<br />\n中意(zung3ji3) 係合心意咁解，&rdquo;中&rdquo;字意思類似 &ldquo;正中下懷&rdquo; 個&rdquo;中&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n「鍾意」是廣東話, 意思是喜歡, 愛. 書面語無此詞語. 但查辭典(台灣教育部國語辭典 http://140.111.1.22/mandr/clc/dict):<br />\n<br />\n「鍾愛」 = 特別疼愛。[北史˙卷十二˙隋煬帝本紀：上美姿儀，少敏慧，高祖及后於諸子中，特所鍾愛。三國演義˙第十六回：惟嚴氏生一女，布最鍾愛。]<br />\n<br />\n「鍾情」 = 專情愛慕。如：一見鍾情。<br />\n至於「中意」, 也是一個正確的書面語, 意思係合意、滿意。[漢書˙卷四十五˙江充傳：奉法不阿，所言中意。初刻拍案驚奇˙卷三：老身虛心冷氣，看他眉頭眼後，常是不中意，受他凌辱的。]<br />\n意思類似「啱聽」.<br />\n<br />\n所以要真的要寫的話, 「鍾意」比較正確. 而且「中意」的「中」讀「種」音(同「中獎」「中傷」, 「中規中距」等情況), 不是讀「鍾」音."},{"pid":"cc124911481870a865b7956317cd04bf2528e5c3","tid":1781053,"uid":247237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f13d99cae9877d6960ac1025691010918513a822","tid":1781053,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597adfab933e400fcd3eefde8349185daf3a8201","tid":1781053,"uid":247237,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"e4b86b80634218599f447e2742ae4f78f1cedcf6","tid":1781053,"uid":25918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"唔會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講有遇過蝦米size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻反面走左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔撚掂 冇發育？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"bb鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c5dfdb6eccf634223366dcae7448df77be6574","tid":1781053,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe5e8a74146d798f5f36767be3943bd8ff7d4a0d","tid":1781053,"uid":327462,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb495848cd519e34f2c2a90b344a937829dd2e66","tid":1781053,"uid":25918,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote"